# @decision DEC-CI-SHAVE-LINT-LF-001
# All TypeScript and JSON sources in @yakcc/shave are LF-canonical on checkout.
# Biome enforces LF; without this, Windows checkouts via core.autocrlf=true
# would deliver CRLF and produce ~125 phantom format-violations on any PR
# that invalidates the shave-lint turbo cache. See packages/seeds/.gitattributes
# for the same fix in a sibling package (#417 / #418).

*.ts text eol=lf
*.tsx text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
